title: Paul McCartney LIVE! at Maida Vale BBC Studios, London, October
description:
I made this album for myself and I have to say I was surprised that I got the audio to sound this good so I decided to share it. I spruced it up a bit, tagged it, and made a nice album cover so that it looks good in iTunes. Macca's bass sounds CRAZY GOOD on here. Info below. Enjoy.


*** ALL TRACKS 320KBPS MP3 ***

*** iTUNES READY, JUST DOWNLOAD, IMPORT, ENJOY ***

*** ALL TAGS (TRACK NUMBER, ALBUM ART, ARTIST, ETC.) EMBEDDED ***

*** AUDIO ADJUSTED FOR GREAT SOUND ***
